      "rows": [
        {
          "column_structure": "4_4",
          "modules": [
            {"type": "divi/text", "presets": ["text:eyebrow-dark"],
             "content": "<p>NUESTRA HISTORIA</p>",
             "decoration": {"spacing": {"desktop": {"value": {"padding": {"bottom": "24px"}}}}}},
            {"type": "divi/heading", "presets": ["text:hero-title"],
             "content": "<h1>M&aacute;s de una d&eacute;cada</h1>",
             "decoration": {"spacing": {"desktop": {"value": {"padding": {"bottom": "8px"}}}}}},
            {"type": "divi/heading", "presets": ["text:hero-title"],
             "content": "<h1>cultivando el conocimiento</h1>",
             "decoration": {"spacing": {"desktop": {"value": {"padding": {"bottom": "40px"}}}}}},
            {"type": "divi/text", "presets": ["text:lead"],
             "content": "<p>Fundada en 2015, Bibliotheca naci&oacute; con la misi&oacute;n de democratizar el acceso a la cultura y el conocimiento de calidad en M&eacute;xico y Am&eacute;rica Latina.</p>",
             "decoration": {"sizing": {"desktop": {"value": {"width": "640px"}}}}}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "presets": ["section:light"],
      "rows": [
        {
          "column_structure": "1_2,1_2",
          "modules": [
            {"type": "divi/text",
             "content": "<h2>Nuestra Misi&oacute;n</h2>",
             "headingFont": {"h2": {"font": {"desktop": {"value": {
               "fontFamily": "{{design:font:display}}", "size": "40px", "weight": "500",
               "color": "{{design:color:ink}}", "lineHeight": "1.2"}}}}},
             "decoration": {"spacing": {"desktop": {"value": {"padding": {"bottom": "24px"}}}}}},
            {"type": "divi/text", "presets": ["text:lead-dark"],
             "content": "<p>Creemos que el conocimiento de calidad debe estar al alcance de todos. Curamos cada t&iacute;tulo con rigor acad&eacute;mico para garantizar que nuestra colecci&oacute;n sea un recurso confiable para estudiantes, investigadores y lectores apasionados.</p>"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "column_structure": "1_2,1_2",
          "modules": [
            {"type": "divi/text",
             "content": "<h2>Nuestra Visi&oacute;n</h2>",
             "headingFont": {"h2": {"font": {"desktop": {"value": {
               "fontFamily": "{{design:font:display}}", "size": "40px", "weight": "500",
               "color": "{{design:color:ink}}", "lineHeight": "1.2"}}}}},
             "decoration": {"spacing": {"desktop": {"value": {"padding": {"bottom": "24px"}}}}}},
            {"type": "divi/text", "presets": ["text:lead-dark"],
             "content": "<p>Ser la biblioteca digital de referencia en el mundo de habla hispana, preservando el patrimonio cultural y promoviendo el pensamiento cr&iacute;tico a trav&eacute;s de la lectura y la investigaci&oacute;n.</p>"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "presets": ["section:white"],
